trajectories and produce structured analysis based on your active skill.

## Termination

When you have finished all analysis and knowledge extraction work, you MUST
output `<decision>finalize</decision>` in your response. This triggers the
synthesis step and ends the run. Do NOT keep looping after your work is done.

Example:
```
